data.description: If you are looking for a pristine home look no further! This is a smoke & pet-free condo. It is move-in ready with fresh paint, new roof (2017), & a new a/c unit (2023). Enjoy the comfort of new carpet & tile flooring (2020) and upgraded fixtures. The fenced paver patio is perfect for outdoor living.This home offers gas heating, a new hot water tank (2022), and all appliances convey. The $210 HOA fee covers a pool, workout facility, clubhouse, & playground/park. Stay connected with weekly security & Block Watch. Monthly utilities are economical: gas $55, electric $52, water/sewer $26.Discover this dog-friendly community with guest parking, new pavement (2023), & an active Association Board. Embrace modern living, community amenities, and a well-maintained property.
